Install Nodejs using the following command
			sudo apt-get install nodejs
	
Install the angular CLI using the following command
			npm install -g  @angular/cli

Create project using the following command
				ng new angularProjectName

Install bootstrap framework on your project using this command in your project directory
				npm install bootstrap â€“save
        
Bulid the project
		ng serve

To Build the project and start the server
			ng serve -o
			
Command to create the component.
	ng generate component yourcomponentName
	
To create a service
	ng g service yourserviceName
	
			

